propel.core.collections.lists

Class ReifiedArrayList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • propel.core.collections.lists.ReifiedArrayList<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.util.Collection<T>, java.util.List<T>, ReifiedList<T>, ReifiedIterable<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SharedList

    public class ReifiedArrayList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ReifiedList<T>
    A type-aware array-backed list that uses similar semantics and strategy to the java.util.ArrayList. This collection allows nulls to be inserted. Instantiate using e.g.: new ReifiedArrayList<String>(){}; -OR- new ReifiedArrayList<String>(String.class);
